Package: linux-soundboard
Version: 1.1.2
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1, libadwaita-1-0, pipewire, policykit-1
Maintainer: germanua <noreply@linuxsoundboard.invalid>
Description: A Linux soundboard with PipeWire virtual mic support
 LinuxSoundBoard is a feature-rich soundboard application for Linux
 with PipeWire virtual microphone support and global hotkey functionality
 via host-installed swhkd on Wayland, with full native X11 support.
 .
 Features:
  - Play sound effects with native Wayland and X11 hotkeys
  - Virtual microphone output via PipeWire
  - Auto-gain normalization (EBU R128)
  - Multiple playback modes
  - GTK4/libadwaita modern UI
